page.title: 14Stuart's day (continued)
page.content: We return back to school,get changed and go home at 3.15pm. I get into the house and get changed to go outside and play with friends at chasey, football or other games like golf. I come back in for my tea at 5.30pm. I eat my tea of potatoes, salad, meat, etc, then brush my teeth. At 6 o'clock I go to the Carnegie Centre in Dunfermline for one hour's training in the swimming pool with Carnegie Swimming Club. I finish at 7 o'clock,come home and watch the t.v. till 9 o'clock. I put my pyjamas on and go to bed to read for about half an hour or so, then fall asleep.
